des: "An easy fun dinner. Serve with cubed bread, ham, sausage, or vegetables."
ins: Stir Cheddar cheese soup, Cheddar cheese, wine, garlic, Worcestershire sauce, and dry mustard together in the top of a double boiler with the water gently simmering over medium-low heat; cook, stirring frequently, until the cheese is melted completely and the mixture is smooth, about 20 minutes
